Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.34,0:00:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.96,0:00:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.81,0:00:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.78,0:00:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.35,0:00:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是關於一個約定的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.95,0:00:38.57,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（吸血鬼女王的戰略究竟是什麼）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.58,0:00:41.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（吸血鬼的女王正在傳訊證人中）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是偉大的魔物女王和為她獻出一切的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位少年的童話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時的我  始終堅信著一切都是從這天開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.82,0:00:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅了拜占庭帝國
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.94,0:01:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並捲入到巴爾幹半島的諸候們的抵抗中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.43,0:01:03.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是德拉庫拉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.97,0:01:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.53,0:01:11.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅馬尼亞的弗蘭德·澤貝休便是一個代表性人物…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.53,0:01:11.69,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（弗蘭德三世：現實中的吸血鬼原形）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.86,0:01:14.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有德拉庫拉嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.74,0:01:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.94,0:01:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤貝休不就是那個公主嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.99,0:01:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜  請大家安靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.01,0:01:24.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭德三世只是電影小說的原型…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.02,0:01:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅拉修女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.14,0:01:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.97,0:01:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我快憋不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  請便
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.97,0:01:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊  別嚇唬人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:42.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是敗給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.74,0:01:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輿論中有關吸血鬼的討論如火如荼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.13,0:01:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不知為何  每當出現這類話題時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.05,0:01:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就會變得一臉不高興
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:01:57.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我那時還不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.49,0:02:02.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那時  他自己也已經忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  我是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:07.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼心煩氣躁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人的故事  在很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我與鏑木曉相識許多年前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就開始的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:55.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}正如內閣官房長官發表的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.22,0:04:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}已確認零號填築地的所有權利都被米娜·澤貝休合法買斷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}政府方面正受到各界追問
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:06.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸血鬼可真有錢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  你真的相信有吸血鬼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有看上週的「正義女神」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說那是真的吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  既然存在吸血鬼的話  那其它的會不會也存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說狼人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:22.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科學怪人之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:29.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由紀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便當外賣來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全上壘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出局了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人  肯定看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.17,0:04:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說沒看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:57.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了  我看到了  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:04:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正馬上就會忘記的  沒關係的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你想怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為曉君…感覺對這方面的事情完全沒興趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.94,0:05:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  由紀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在擔心我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然找藉口翹課
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲鈍男
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.62,0:05:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三枝同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於會計報告  有點事情想問問你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能來一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  會長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.48,0:05:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧你那沒出息的熊樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你要我上她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.51,0:05:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢那樣的話  我就揍死你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:05:57.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個好女孩兒啊  三枝同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你為什麼不對她認真點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:12.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真…認真什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:15.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種意義上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.65,0:06:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道該怎麼說才好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.66,0:06:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的變了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的你  應該更冷淡的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.15,0:06:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  這也是沒辦法的事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了找到了  久世
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放學後能借用一下視聽教室嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動用一下你跟學生會關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是不可以  不過你們要用來做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜公主又要舉辦見面會了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.21,0:06:54.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想用大畫面的電視收看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了那種事的話  不許
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.92,0:06:57.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不可能存在吸血鬼之類的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.94,0:06:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被娛樂媒體牽著鼻子走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏑木你也說兩句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也想看的吧  小米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小米娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是在求吐槽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小米娜不就是現在成為輿論話題的那個吸血鬼女王嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.34,0:07:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「啊」你妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.74,0:07:20.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是還在正義女神裡被人採訪了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:23.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對那種事沒什麼興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那節目  還有新聞我都沒看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.26,0:07:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊…喂  鏑木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是吸血鬼的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這是怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.93,0:08:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.45,0:08:11.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人真的不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:19.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.50,0:09:21.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也感到很驚奇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:27.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說頭部的傷是很可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而今天也出現了這種症狀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.56,0:09:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得聽醫生的話  要好好治療才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:38.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:40.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那答應我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:45.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把今天的事告訴醫生  好好接受診斷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.97,0:09:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的  我會去看醫生的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真點嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:14.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其一  啜取世人之血
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.31,0:10:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其二  宿業之不死身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其三  聚集亂世之鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:33.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜·澤貝休？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指吾身為吸血鬼的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.38,0:10:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是在問吾是否真的米娜·澤貝休
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.97,0:10:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論哪個問題答案都不會變
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:53.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾是如假包換的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我說你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.43,0:10:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不等我說完嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:03.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:11.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這身衣服走起路太麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別以為吾總是會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要來我這
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那時又為什麼會哭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子是真的什麼都不記得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.69,0:11:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會…對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:15.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  已經開始了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.55,0:12:18.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那是別的人做的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.02,0:12:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著這機會的人可多著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:27.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}萬分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}由於附近發生了原因不明的爆炸  列車暫緩行駛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,0:12:37.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢  想殺吾的人可多著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅有人類  還有那些非人生物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以突然間搞出剛剛那種襲擊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會有這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論怎麼說  吾也不會那麼簡單地死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許也要到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遮光凝膠的效果快要沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遮光凝膠？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是用於防止太陽光破壞吾細胞的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩一分鐘的藥效了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.23,0:13:11.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾會變成灰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.46,0:13:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…不要說得那麼輕鬆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.58,0:13:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.71,0:13:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說這裡就有那凝膠了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  為啥我要陪你到這個程度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.72,0:13:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才想知道呢  公主小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.60,0:13:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這衣服吾一個人可脫不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到吾裸體後  沒有自信能保持鎮靜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會對你這小鬼的身體有興趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:13:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的…小鬼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼的身體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也的確…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  塗上去也要我來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦  你不是對小鬼的身體滿不在乎的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.39,0:14:17.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你經常會這樣子被襲擊的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.96,0:14:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子還一個人出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.59,0:14:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:45.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小指的約定  在呼喚吾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.96,0:14:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我決定來賭一把	
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.57,0:14:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但似乎是我輸了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.64,0:15:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.77,0:15:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是警察
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:10.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近發生了炸彈恐怖襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在這裡做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.90,0:15:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能問你們一點東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也挺在行的嘛  看出這伙人是刺客
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.80,0:15:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聞到的  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人類嗎  是哪裡派過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.22,0:15:51.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了  也不用勉強你回答了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下吾就能讓你自覺地說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.44,0:16:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地看著吧  這就是真正的吾  吸血鬼的女王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那個是曉君吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那邊去的話  誰也無法對吾下手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾對你表示感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是吸血鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.02,0:16:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾一開始就這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.84,0:16:46.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要突然出現  說要在那邊建立國家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.53,0:16:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了做戰鬥的準備  大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那吾也問一句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.22,0:16:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在幸福嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:04.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失去了記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.91,0:17:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年這個時候  我發生了事故
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.99,0:17:14.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好笑吧  十六年的記憶什麼都沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  儘管是這樣的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.31,0:17:21.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然有願意待在我身邊的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:24.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有關心我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是幸福吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  吾要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:18:00.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前會哭是因為看到你  覺得開心而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:19.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小的是奉命來為公主殿下帶路的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要到哪去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我們的組織那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.42,0:18:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要殺人滅口嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊是夜之領域
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.84,0:18:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在日光下生活的你是禁止進入的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看著我啊  公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪個血族的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.82,0:18:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.27,0:19:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  這事跟那人無關
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人就這麼重要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.04,0:19:33.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  給我死一邊去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:40.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…要哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公…主…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭啦  我跟你約定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.62,0:20:00.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會保護你的  我會一直在你身邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:01.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…不要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:15.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能  他是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.84,0:20:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地之一族
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.36,0:20:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一個關於約定的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.20,0:21:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偉大的魔物女王與為她獻出一切的少年間的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.25,0:21:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一段美麗而又淒慘的愛情童話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.34,0:23:07.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與吸血鬼女僕共舞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.47,0:23:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.81,0:23:08.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}（大概在嘟嘟囔囔地說著夢話）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.18,0:23:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.58,0:23:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢把公主殿下全身都塗得黏乎乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.25,0:23:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以死謝罪吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.48,0:23:15.73,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（這把電鋸的名字和奈葉的魔導器名字Raising Heart同一發音）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.15,0:23:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  只有剛進去那一下會痛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.18,0:23:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.44,0:23:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開…開什麼玩笑  那平胸女的洗衣板
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.02,0:23:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算摸了也不會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.78,0:23:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平胸女的洗衣板啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這狼人砍成三塊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.07,0:23:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  咦  等…等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.25,0:23:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
